    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride! This vehicle is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a functional, honest car that gets the job done. While it shows some expected wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a solid choice for daily commutes or as a reliable second vehicle. It's a great opportunity to own a quality brand at a very accessible price point!",
