      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The engine starts consistently and the car is fully drivable, though you may notice some typical wear and tear consistent with its age, including minor interior scuffs and some fading on the exterior paint. It has been maintained to a functional standard, but a new owner might want to address a few minor cosmetic issues and keep up with upcoming scheduled maintenance. This is a solid, honest car for someone who needs a dependable daily driver without the premium price tag of a showroom-ready model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
