    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is primarily recommended as a project car or for parts. The engine requires significant mechanical attention due to persistent leaks and a lack of compression in one cylinder, and the transmission is currently slipping. Visually, the car has substantial rust on the frame and body panels, along with significant interior damage. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed from its location.",
      "price": 6500.0,
